00:00:08,759 --> 00:00:09,979
I really appreciate you coming.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:13,661
So what does that long-winded title even mean, really?

5
00:00:14,221 --> 00:00:16,242
I mean, I think we can all think of games that we've played

6
00:00:16,262 --> 00:00:18,564
where we encountered characters that sort of stuck

7
00:00:18,584 --> 00:00:20,344
in our minds that we thought about,

8
00:00:20,384 --> 00:00:22,065
and we wondered what they were thinking late at night,

9
00:00:22,105 --> 00:00:24,006
and maybe they remember that horrible thing

10
00:00:24,046 --> 00:00:24,787
we said to them once.

11
00:00:24,867 --> 00:00:27,548
And we can also remember games where we just didn't have

12
00:00:27,588 --> 00:00:28,789
that attachment to certain characters.

13
00:00:28,809 --> 00:00:30,189
We sort of got through the entire game.

14
00:00:31,010 --> 00:00:33,530
