This is something that I have had a lot of experience in my career thinking about and

24
00:00:58,643 --> 00:00:59,083
working on.

25
00:00:59,604 --> 00:01:04,325
A lot of my career was at Telltale Games where I worked on Walking Dead Season 1, 400 Days,

26
00:01:04,365 --> 00:01:06,725
the DLC episode, and Season 2.

27
00:01:07,826 --> 00:01:11,086
I was the guy who designed the train puzzle, so for the three of you in here that like

