00:18:06,806 --> 00:18:08,067
against their own pragmatism.

447
00:18:09,188 --> 00:18:12,311
It's a really interesting way to mix up the things

448
00:18:12,331 --> 00:18:13,172
that your player cares about.

449
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:15,021
So here's an early idea.

