00:18:15,061 --> 00:18:16,942
I had an early idea for Tales from the Borderlands.

451
00:18:16,962 --> 00:18:18,203
We were gonna get unlockable weapons.

452
00:18:18,283 --> 00:18:19,984
So when you played Tales from the Borderlands,

453
00:18:20,405 --> 00:18:21,786
you could unlock certain weapons,

454
00:18:21,806 --> 00:18:22,646
you could put them in Borderlands 2,

455
00:18:22,826 --> 00:18:24,407
and you'd have like a unique gun or whatever.

456
00:18:25,448 --> 00:18:26,949
And my design was to actually tie them

