00:19:53,778 --> 00:19:54,098
goes away.

498
00:19:55,567 --> 00:19:58,169
What was really interesting though is that 63% of people

499
00:19:58,189 --> 00:20:00,150
did anything it took to keep everyone happy,

500
00:20:01,671 --> 00:20:03,032
which is really, really interesting

501
00:20:03,092 --> 00:20:05,173
because this is a super systems-heavy game

502
00:20:05,253 --> 00:20:07,714
and you get a really, really tangible mechanical benefit

503
00:20:08,215 --> 00:20:09,575
for basically screwing somebody over

